{"tid":1794760,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"【江永祥邏輯】其實兜巴星黑警都只是「Happy New Year!」","createTime":"2019-12-23T11:00:34.000Z","updateTime":"2019-12-23T11:05:23.000Z","uid":79563,"like":3,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"a90181e4c2eaf813a2e1d5e3a306c1caf47769b0","tid":1794760,"uid":79563,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-23T11:00:34.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=cPRb2aBqOJA&amp;t=12m25s\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3DcPRb2aBqOJA%26t%3D12m25s&d=HJ1jiXHXfxJ2%2FxolOfbUwSaGrLhPWbn%2F%2Bskqqi57m1s%3D&h=fcdab5bc\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=cPRb2aBqOJA&amp;t=12m25s</a><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/e-paper/20141224/large/1419406035_80af.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20141224%2Flarge%2F1419406035_80af.jpg&h=ba098df6&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n一名「藍帽子」警員隨即步入人群中勸喻青年離開，從無綫電視拍攝的片段可見，有人懷疑態度囂張，與警員推撞，而背向鏡頭的警員則兩度掌摑面向鏡頭、瘦身材的金髮少年。在旁群眾一度起哄，至最後在警員勸喻下離去。<br />\n<br />\n事件傳出後隨即惹來社會各界對警方掌摑市民的濫權疑雲，警方於2002年1月1日回應指，並未收到任何市民被警員不禮貌的投訴，而時任西九龍總區副指揮官古樹鴻則於1月2日的記者會指，並無警務人員被掌摑，只是有青年「用手輕拍警員面頰，並向警員說『OK! OK! Happy New Year!』（好！好！新年快樂！）」而該名警員亦只是用手「㩒住」青年，以免他在地上拾起螢光棒投擲。"},{"pid":"f80ed02a8808bcd40cde4d6dd1a6ed1a9c2433e2","tid":1794760,"uid":79563,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-12-23T11:02:32.000Z","msg":"江永祥：市民向警方講聲唔該借歪就可以解決碰撞問題<br />\n<br />\nOh really?<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/NfGGtGn.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FNfGGtGn.gif&h=23e039d4&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"436ee4f5c922cffc13f2afccdd7cf5773677da77","tid":1794760,"uid":104258,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"f80ed02a8808bcd40cde4d6dd1a6ed1a9c2433e2","tid":1794760,"uid":79563,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-12-23T11:02:32.000Z","msg":"江永祥：市民向警方講聲唔該借歪就可以解決碰撞問題<br />\n<br />\nOh really?<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/NfGGtGn.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FNfGGtGn.gif&h=23e039d4&s={SIZE}\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-12-23T11:04:01.000Z","msg":"示威者只是用腳輕輕推開警員"},{"pid":"60e66aeaee3d97f55a793c64bc5bade997588647","tid":1794760,"uid":79563,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"436ee4f5c922cffc13f2afccdd7cf5773677da77","tid":1794760,"uid":104258,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"f80ed02a8808bcd40cde4d6dd1a6ed1a9c2433e2","tid":1794760,"uid":79563,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-12-23T11:02:32.000Z","msg":"江永祥：市民向警方講聲唔該借歪就可以解決碰撞問題<br />\n<br />\nOh really?<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/NfGGtGn.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FNfGGtGn.gif&h=23e039d4&s={SIZE}\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-12-23T11:04:01.000Z","msg":"示威者只是用腳輕輕推開警員"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-23T11:05:23.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://cdn.thestandnews.com/media/photos/cache/popo-13_8BJJg_1200x0.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thestandnews.com%2Fmedia%2Fphotos%2Fcache%2Fpopo-13_8BJJg_1200x0.png&h=10153fe6&s={SIZE}\" />"}]}